androidx.arch.core.executor

Class TaskExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • androidx.arch.core.executor.TaskExecutor
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArchTaskExecutor, DefaultTaskExecutor, TaskExecutorWithFakeMainThread

    public abstract class TaskExecutor
extends java.lang.Object
    A task executor that can divide tasks into logical groups.

    It holds a collection a executors for each group of task.

    TODO: Don't use this from outside, we don't know what the API will look like yet.

Generated javadoc for the new package structure to make it clearer which packages are bundled with the Android operating system, and which are packaged with your app's APK. Going forward, the android.* package hierarchy will be reserved for Android packages that ship with the operating system; other packages will be issued in the new androidx.* package hiearchy.
